summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the dismissal of proceedings pertaining to certain tracts and parcels of land situate between Jackson Street and Yesler Way and between East Jefferson Street and East Cherry Street; from that certain condemnation proceedings for the laying off, opening, widening extending and establishing of 27th Avenue South and other streets and avenues as provided for by Ordinance No. 78109, being Cause No. 423901 of the Superior Court of the State of Washington for King County.
